title: Super BlackJack 5.8
description:
Super BlackJack is a blackjack training tool designed to prepare
you for real casino play. You&#039;ll learn basic strategy, the
secrets of card counting and how the house rules affect your
game. Super BlackJack will show you the right move to make in
any situation by making recommendations as you play. You&#039;ll
always know exactly when to double down, when to split, when to
hit, and when to stand. Play against the dealer or practice the
customizable playing strategies with built-in strategy drills
and flash cards. A long list of game options allows you to
tailor the house rules to your liking.
